課程概述 Course Description
       為學生提供可能性和統計的理論的基本規律，重點在工程應用To provide students with fundamentals of the theory of probability and statistics, with an emphasis on engineering applications    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Learning fundamental Concepts of probabilityLearning mathematical models of statisticsLearning inferential statistics and engineering applications 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
